- ðŸ“‹ Event schema v2 (duration_ms, validation events)
- ðŸ“‹ Preliminary gateway context (instrumentation for v1.2.0 design)
- **Focus:** Enable mcp-n8n Phase 1 feedback loop

### v1.2.0 ðŸŽ¯ Week 7-10 (Gateway Integration - Phased Betas)
- **Beta 1 (Week 7):** Gateway-aware capabilities + preview artifact tool
- **Beta 2 (Week 9):** Telemetry resource + multi-step preview + performance
- **GA (Week 10):** Complete documentation + production hardening
- **Focus:** Platform-layer maturation, unblock mcp-n8n Phase 2 early

### v1.3.0+ ðŸš€ Week 11-14 (Dynamic Discovery & Context Bus)
- ðŸ“‹ Dynamic capability discovery (hot-reload generators)
- ðŸ“‹ Workflow coordination primitives (transactions, rollback)
- ðŸ“‹ Context bus integration (when platform provides it)
- ðŸ“‹ SLSA Level 3 provenance
- **Focus:** Runtime extensibility + distributed platform infrastructure



